 A http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/native_client/tests/threads/main_thread_pthread_exit_test.c?r1=2717&amp;r2=2716&amp;pathrev=2717

Fix pthread_exit for the main thread.
When pthread_exit is called from the main thread, call exit() after waiting for all the other threads instead of thread_exit(). This ensures the application termination code is executed correctly.
